our approach may generalise to other\nproblems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Feb 2018 20:02:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 17 Aug 2018 10:19:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-20"}
