e sets are relevant in practice, suggesting\nthat the active sets is the appropriate level of abstraction for a learning\nalgorithm to target.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Feb 2018 23:24:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 22 Mar 2018 18:54:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 4 Jun 2018 23:14:09 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 16 Jan 2019 20:28:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-01-18"}
